   <concept outputclass="Section" id="Section_1352_270_70_T48_50650452161">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">1352.270-70</ph> Period of performance.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">As prescribed in 48 CFR 1370.101, insert the following clause:
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="HD1">Period of Performance (APR 2010)
</p>
                                    <p outputclass="List1">(a) The base period of performance of this contract is from ____ through ____. If an option is exercised, the period of performance shall be extended through the end of that option period.
</p>
                                    <p outputclass="List1">(b) The option periods that may be exercised are as follows:
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="DIV">
                                       
                                          <table frame="all" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
               <tgroup cols="3" outputclass="FormatA">
                  <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colsep="0"/>
                  <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colsep="0"/>
                  <colspec colnum="3" colname="3" colsep="0"/>
                  <thead>
                     <row rowsep="1">
                                                <entry colname="1">Period 
</entry>
                                                <entry colname="2">Start date 
</entry>
                                                <entry colname="3">End date
</entry>
                                             </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                     <row rowsep="1">
                                                <entry colname="1" align="left">Option I</entry>
                                                <entry colname="2" align="right"/>
                                                <entry colname="3" align="right"/>
                                             </row>
                     <row rowsep="1">
                                                <entry colname="1" align="left">Option II</entry>
                                                <entry colname="2" align="right"/>
                                                <entry colname="3" align="right"/>
                                             </row>
                     <row rowsep="1">
                                                <entry colname="1" align="left">Option III</entry>
                                                <entry colname="2" align="right"/>
                                                <entry colname="3" align="right"/>
                                             </row>
                     <row rowsep="1">
                                                <entry colname="1" align="left">Option IV</entry>
                                                <entry colname="2" align="right"/>
                                                <entry colname="3" align="right"/>
                                             </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
                                       
                                    </p>
                                    <p outputclass="List1">(c) The notice requirements for unilateral exercise of option periods are set out in FAR 52.217-9.</p>
                                 <p xtrc="HD3">(End of clause)
</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
